name: text_diff
description: Compare two files or directories with diff — a unified patch-style diff, a side-by-side view, a recursive directory compare, and an ignore-whitespace mode. Use to see what differs between two files, compare trees, or produce a patch.
kind: tool
tags: [text, diff, compare, patch, files, directories]
use_when: [compare two files, what changed between files, side by side diff, compare two directories, make a patch, diff ignoring whitespace, show differences]
